(2556, 1, '2018-11-30 04:33:45', '2018-11-30 04:33:45', '<div id=\"pl-2556\"  class=\"panel-layout\" ><div id=\"pg-2556-0\"  class=\"panel-grid panel-has-style\"  data-style=\"{&quot;mobile_padding&quot;:&quot;0px 0px 0px 0px&quot;,&quot;background_image_attachment&quot;:false,&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;,&quot;cell_alignment&quot;:&quot;flex-start&quot;}\"  data-ratio=\"0.33333333\"  data-ratio-direction=\"right\" ><div class=\"panel-row-style panel-row-style-for-2556-0\" ><div id=\"pgc-2556-0-0\"  class=\"panel-grid-cell\"  data-weight=\"0.7639320250534\" ><div id=\"panel-2556-0-0-0\" class=\"so-panel widget widget_text panel-first-child panel-last-child\" data-index=\"0\" data-style=\"{&quot;background_image_attachment&quot;:false,&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;,&quot;margin&quot;:&quot;0px 0px 0px 0px&quot;}\" >			<div class=\"textwidget\"><p>Indian Institute of Management (IIM) Ranchi is the ninth member of the IIM family. Established by the Government of India in December 2009, we made a modest beginning with 44 students in Post Graduate Programme in Management. With the active support of the Government of India, Government of Jharkhand, Mentoring of IIM Calcutta and strategic guidance of Board of Governors of IIM Ranchi, we have emerged as one of the fastest growing IIMs with a combined strength of 500 students in various programs.</p>\n<p>We aspire to develop IIM Ranchi as one of the top 10 management institutes in the Asian Region within next 10 years through teaching excellence and thought leadership. At IIM Ranchi we plan to attain thought leadership through fusion of eastern wisdom and western processes and focusing on research which is both rigorous and contextually relevant. We also develop teaching excellence through participant centered learning including technologically enabled and experiential pedagogies.</p>\n</div>\n		</div></div><div id=\"pgc-2556-0-1\"  class=\"panel-grid-cell\"  data-weight=\"0.2360679749466\